            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Score the <strong>camembert </strong>in a criss-cross pattern</p><p>Spread the <strong>remaining garlic </strong>over the scored camembert</p><p>Top with the<strong> cranberry sauce </strong>and<strong> half </strong>the<strong> chopped walnuts </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> loaded camembert</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
