    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap the <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>and cut into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> squares</p><p>Line a baking tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Add 1<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2]</span> <strong>pastry square<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> to the baking tray, prick all over with a fork (this will stop it getting a soggy bottom!) and top with the <strong>loaded camembert</strong></p>",
